data.description:
Discover an exceptional investment opportunity that perfectly marries comfort, convenience, and potential returns! Nestled in the heart of Dallas, Texas, just moments away from the vibrant Bishop Arts neighborhood, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom full duplex has undergone an extensive transformation, presenting an irresistible prospect for seasoned investors.

Current tenant at $1645, below market rate. Lease till Feb '24. We kindly request that you refrain from disturbing the current tenants who reside in one of the units. The other unit is occupied by the property owner, ensuring attentive management and Schedule showing via agent. Don't miss out!
